title: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export data from a table that contains a highlight or map, an exception is thrown.
EB: When exporting the data in the table, the expected result is that the data is successfully exported.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, please follow these steps:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Attempt to export the data from a table that contains a highlight or map.
3. Observe the exception that is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
